dashboard_elements.body_text:
CATs Usage by Citizens

The KPI included are:
- # of BC government pages viewed;
- # of Pages related to a Ministry.



# of CATs Visitors

The Term of Use (TOU) page is the first page whenever citizens use CATs. Therefore the # of TOU pages viewed is how many sessions that citizens used CATs terminal. It is reported as the approximation to the # of citizens, although a citizen could conduct multiple sessions and click the TOU page multiple times.
* This TOU page data is available only since Aug 22, 2019.

CATs effectiveness

- The % of citizens landed on at least one meaningful page.
- In order to land on one meaningful page, how many pages do Citizens have to navigate.
* A meaningful page is when a page is owned by a ministry or the url is for a downloadable form or document.
